{"tid":972630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"百萬行最高人氣 MIRROR幫ViuTV挫無綫","createTime":"2019-01-07T13:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T16:00:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf19634cdd614180f4001028997d3de0a0e591b3","tid":972630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190107/20585214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F20585214&d=za12ywSivCnp80l6%2BeUfg9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=974d8175\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190107%2F20585214&h=f092c712\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190107/20585214</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年01月07日 <br />\n<br />\n百萬行最高人氣<br />\nMIRROR幫ViuTV挫無綫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190107/large/07ec2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190107%2Flarge%2F07ec2p1.jpg&h=bf4c2dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男團MIRROR昨早參與在中環舉行的百萬行，吸引大批fans到場支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫、ViuTV和新城昨日參與中環百萬行，雖然無綫人多勢眾，派出由高層鄭善強、杜之克及樂易玲領軍的90人隊伍，較ViuTV總經理魯庭暉領軍的60人隊伍多，但無綫今年卡士甚弱，為人熟悉的藝人就只有陳煒、黎諾懿、徐榮、陳庭欣和安德尊等，相反ViuTV派出人氣男子組合MIRROR，吸引半百fans到場打氣及舉牌支持，並以姜濤的fans最多，當MIRROR入場時，一班fans叫個不停，但無綫一隊行入會場時，有市民皺眉說：「都唔識嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬德鐘因家人缺席<br />\n<br />\n對於MIRROR聲勢浩大，身為隊長的Lokman說：「多謝，朋友畀面，我哋之前都驚見唔到佢哋（歌迷），佢哋太熱情，喺港鐵站已經捕住我哋。」陳安立曾與黃心美傳緋聞，對於心美與薛芷倫大仔馬桂烽拍拖，陳安立說：「我戥佢開心，不過佢冇回應，我都唔講咁多。」<br />\n<br />\n昨日馬德鐘本有份行百萬行，但因家人身體不適入院而缺席，樂易玲說：「佢因屋企有人唔舒服入醫院，凌晨5點幾打畀我話嚟唔到，我應承咗佢唔講得乜事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190107/large/07ec2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190107%2Flarge%2F07ec2p2.jpg&h=31c32a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐榮（左）和黎諾懿雖然現身撐無綫活動，但人氣輸給MIRROR。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190107/large/07ec2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190107%2Flarge%2F07ec2p3.jpg&h=fd692ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳庭欣（左）昨早要由男友叫她起身，會合陳煒及江嘉敏（右）參與百萬行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳煒留意亞視裁員<br />\n<br />\n說到新組合MIRROR人氣勁搶盡風頭，樂易玲表示：「都有留意望吓，覺得幾好幾靚仔。」可有意撬眾人過檔？樂易玲說：「唔好咁。」提到無綫可以組隊力撼，樂易玲表示：「同Herman（何哲圖）講，其實我哋公司都有好多後生仔同訓練班學員，Herman唔做我做啦。」亞視近日又裁員，亞姐出身的陳煒說：「希望唔好有呢啲事，就快過年啲人會好徬徨。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：卓寶花、黃曉妍<br />\n攝影：陳俊強  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n單身孫佳君約女友嘆茶<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n洪金寶唔敢惡孫仔"},{"pid":"8b38ef3197388dc9929ff60021aa9a1c1e7798bf","tid":972630,"uid":13653,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"但無綫一隊行入會場時，有市民皺眉說：「都唔識嘅！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f5350832344797292414c1f4e4763d67bfea4e","tid":972630,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"亞視裁員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44837c1c2cf333982c13a1ef4278303a797eb847","tid":972630,"uid":174420,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"咁玩啦<br />\n呢隊垃圾打得贏tvb?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade42618f0acb2111e8dac44108fefee65701db9","tid":972630,"uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b38ef3197388dc9929ff60021aa9a1c1e7798bf","tid":972630,"uid":13653,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"但無綫一隊行入會場時，有市民皺眉說：「都唔識嘅！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"所謂既「市民」係唔係指 姜濤果50名fans之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9624c4e2b3bb54aaf003f3785ebd3b48ae5f8340","tid":972630,"uid":53705,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"44837c1c2cf333982c13a1ef4278303a797eb847","tid":972630,"uid":174420,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"咁玩啦<br />\n呢隊垃圾打得贏tvb?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"家陣香港 根本無出名既男團<br />\n呢隊野已經算係香港最紅男團<br />\n<br />\n不過其實除左姜濤, 應該無乜人識其他成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c87cced168373d2055b112222ffb3795f27751","tid":972630,"uid":31693,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"昨日馬德鐘本有份行百萬行，但因家人身體不適入院而缺席，<span style=\"color: red;\">樂易玲說：「佢因屋企有人唔舒服入醫院，凌晨5點幾打畀我話嚟唔到，我應承咗佢唔講得乜事。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cacc0ccb3286b6f5ed5a2afd1e55b9f3d0961d","tid":972630,"uid":148606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49f5350832344797292414c1f4e4763d67bfea4e","tid":972630,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"亞視裁員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"原來未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}